name: Gourmet Mushroom Burger 50 gm 8 Pcs
description:
DescriptionAnother must
try addition to Gourmet's vegan range is our new mushroom burger. Mushrooms are a great way to replace meat,
as they have a dense texture and hold together to create a meaty bite. The meatless burger patties are made of plump
mushrooms, freek, oat flakes, bread crumbs and spinach for a juicy consistency and seasoned with a blend of herbs (
thyme, rosemary & oregano). Mustard, garlic & onion are also added for a scrumptious taste. If you are not a fan of
meatless burgers, think again!
Foodie Tip: For a wholesome bite, place the mushroom burger in Gourmet burger buns,
top with sliced onions, tomatoes, avocados and your preferred cheese.

description:

Gourmet's handcrafted Dip It range.
